title: Formula 1 2012 Inside Grand Prix Round Nine Great Britain
description:
Formula 1 2012 Inside Grand Prix Round Nine Great Britain

Inside Grand Prix precedes each round of the Formula One World Championship with      
interviews of the drivers and those behind the scenes. The latest news and technical  
features as well as historical reports make Inside GP the programme of record when it 
comes to the worlds most important motor racing series.


Duration : ~26 Min 
Format : AVI 
Video codec : XviD, 768x432, 25 fps, ~1750 kbps  
Audio codec : MP3, 48 KHz 2 ch, 128kbps
